"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Splinterlands is a card collection game, which is full of fun through rich race design and card function setting. He allows people to collect, fight and trade cards through blockchain encryption. And through rich market functions to meet the needs of players' interactive cards.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/INnwthCqSEg0Fa07ISIXQ.png?height=651&width=333)\\n\\nHowever, many new players are not familiar with the rich content of the game when they first enter the game, so they don't know how to choose their own lineup. So today I will recommend a set of invincible magic lineup.\\n\\nEarth magic attack.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/DxEzXOfT49n46XhyDetHA.png?height=247&width=322)\\n\\nFirst, we need a magic lineup. The core is this card.\\n\\nWith the help of the Lord, the 2-point spell attack can reach 3-point attack, which allows him to kill the opponent's tank as soon as possible together with other cards.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/HlVG5GLGMk4-g7-nZi4Xt.png?height=459&width=335)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ERHg4-8zqvuaMgAmta6m4.png?height=780&width=1499)\\n\\nWithout considering the points, he can form a terrible lineup with other cards and beat your opponent 100%.\\n\\nThere are three tips for you\\n\\n1. Don't let cards with only 1 HP stand in the first and last positions;\\n2. You can rent this card\\n3. The front row is dominated by cards with high blood volume. I like this one best within 30-points:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/qMoPuaqLIT0u21tmJtUEG.png?height=436&width=316)\\n\\nFinally, I wish you success!\",\"timestamp\":1633849203,\"title\":\"Magic is invincible! In splinterlands. Gospel of new players\"},\"digest\":\"iT8YY4VwqZ8M3P4jWYlM87064LFClrfXuhod7mppK8A\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x45c960d3342f778939bd4E121C0d07Bf3692ca23\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"fIQSa2eHyJiE57-Ug5-rlO93atr7_J38QWTIwn2BoJ4\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3oyGqOJmX2Awz_Vb9e2SflZW5rCfKecsDcSexH_MJdE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"mu0A9r0Kghc7lODmXy_dM0OePiqHRTf2XskR-47RlDjhsaNXn-wqD2xj6bG9EYHJyMsYJIa83vMfG2uSv_ouZQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xac2a10309a94208944abbd6e6766c770122390c4e6cb3a9d9f2ab04d5c956b5c660470b07ba9274a20ea667145984ceaf1eed3bf40c1a7d9c7886b2c4980ec621b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"fIQSa2eHyJiE57-Ug5-rlO93atr7_J38QWTIwn2BoJ4\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3oyGqOJmX2Awz_Vb9e2SflZW5rCfKecsDcSexH_MJdE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"iT8YY4VwqZ8M3P4jWYlM87064LFClrfXuhod7mppK8A\"}"